Package: ii-material-sddm
Architecture: all
Depends: sddm
Recommends: qt6-5compat-dev | libqt5graphicaleffects5
Suggests: acl
Description: Material Design SDDM login theme
 ii-material-sddm is a clean Material Design theme for the SDDM display
 manager. It features a customizable color scheme via colors.json, support
 for Matugen integration, blur effects (requires qt6-5compat), and a set
 of QML components for clock, user selector, session selector, password
 field, toolbar, and virtual keyboard.
 .
 Optional features:
  - Blur effects require qt6-5compat
  - Matugen color integration requires acl
